---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Now – Victor Thuo"
	description="What I'm focused on right now. Updated March 2026."
>
	<!-- Page Header -->
	<section class="py-20 reveal">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
			<p class="label-arch text-silver-400 mb-4">Now</p>
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-display text-silver-900 dark:text-silver-100 mb-6">
				Now
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg text-silver-400 font-sans" style="font-weight: 300;">
				What I'm focused on right now.
			</p>
			<p class="text-sm text-silver-600 font-sans mt-2">
				Last updated March 2026
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Current Focus -->
	<section class="py-16 reveal">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<!-- Item 1 -->
				<div class="flex gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-silver-200 dark:border-silver-800">
					<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-clay rounded-full mt-2"></div>
					<div class="flex-grow">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-silver-900 dark:text-silver-100 mb-2">
							Healthcare UX & Complexity
						</h3>
						<p class="text-silver-400 font-sans" style="font-weight: 300;">
							Deep-diving into how to design systems that serve both clinicians and administrators in modern healthcare technology. Researching patterns for handling regulatory complexity without burdening users.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Item 2 -->
				<div class="flex gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-silver-200 dark:border-silver-800">
					<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-clay rounded-full mt-2"></div>
					<div class="flex-grow">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-silver-900 dark:text-silver-100 mb-2">
							AI-Driven Design Tools
						</h3>
						<p class="text-silver-400 font-sans" style="font-weight: 300;">
							Exploring how AI is reshaping the design process. Particularly interested in tools that enhance designer productivity without replacing strategic thinking, and how to design for AI-assisted workflows.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Item 3 -->
				<div class="flex gap-4 pb-6 border-b border-silver-200 dark:border-silver-800">
					<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-clay rounded-full mt-2"></div>
					<div class="flex-grow">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-silver-900 dark:text-silver-100 mb-2">
							Building This Portfolio
						</h3>
						<p class="text-silver-400 font-sans" style="font-weight: 300;">
							Designing and building this site as a living showcase of my work. Using Astro, Tailwind, and a typography-forward aesthetic to practice what I preach about minimal, strategic design.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Item 4 -->
				<div class="flex gap-4">
					<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-clay rounded-full mt-2"></div>
					<div class="flex-grow">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display font-semibold text-silver-900 dark:text-silver-100 mb-2">
							Writing & Perspectives
						</h3>
						<p class="text-silver-400 font-sans" style="font-weight: 300;">
							Publishing perspectives on design leadership, behavior change, and the gap between what we design and what actually gets adopted. Focusing on practical insights from enterprise work.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- What is Now? -->
	<section class="py-16 border-t border-silver-200 dark:border-silver-800 reveal">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
			<p class="text-silver-400 font-sans leading-relaxed" style="font-weight: 300;">
				This page is inspired by the <a href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-silver-800 dark:text-silver-200 hover:text-clay transition-colors font-semibold">Now page movement</a>. The idea is simple: share what you're actually focused on right now, not your job title or full bio. It's a snapshot of priorities and interests at a specific moment in time. If you have your own Now page, let me know—I'd love to see what you're working on.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
